title: Kish-Air Kish F.C.
text:
Kish-Air Kish Football Club is an Iranian <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Kish%2C%20Iran">Kish</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. They currently compete in the <a href="Hormozogan">Hormozogan</a> Provincial League.
